type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Fees To Be Paid Node Missing

definition.text: A Fees To Be Paid node was expected but not found at the node where the error originated.

translations.text: Ödenecek Ücretler ( Fees To Be Paid ) düğümü bekleniyordu ancak hatanın kaynaklandığı düğümde bulunamadı.
Ein Fees To Be Paid -Knoten wurde erwartet, aber nicht an dem Knoten gefunden, an dem der Fehler auftrat.

paragraphs.text: Fees To Be Paid Node Missing

translations.text: Ödenecek,Ücretler Düğüm Eksik. ( Fees To Be Paid Node Missing )
Fees To Be Paid Node -Knoten fehlt (Fees To Be Paid Node Missing)

paragraphs.text: Add the missing node and try again.

translations.text: Eksik düğümü ekleyin ve tekrar deneyin.
Fügen Sie den fehlenden Knoten hinzu und versuchen Sie es erneut.
